FAQ'S

Frequently Asked Questions

Find quick answers to the most common support questions

Ready to get started?

Spots are limited - we work with a select number of founders each month to focus on quality & results. Secure your place below.

Apply Now

What makes CineMorph Media different from other agencies or freelancers?

We don't just "edit videos." We build your entire personal brand as an asset - uncovering your story, shaping your positioning, and producing content that compounds over time. Most agencies focus on output. We focus on building cultural relevance and authority.

Who do you work with?

We work with ambitious founders, SaaS and Web3 startups, and agencies that want content built for growth. Our clients care about long-term brand equity, not just quick edits or trend-chasing. If you’re looking for cheap videos, we’re not the right fit. If you want content that elevates your brand, drives attention, and positions you as a leader in your space, that’s where we come in.

What’s included in your packages?

Every package blends creativity + strategy. That means every client gets: • A dedicated editor who knows your brand. • A creative team focused on video and motion. • Strategy calls to align content with your goals. Platform-ready edits built for reach and engagement. In short: everything you need to turn raw footage into high-performing content that builds authority and drives results.

How soon will I see results?

Most clients start noticing traction with more views, engagement and inquiries within 30 to 60 days. Our focus is on long-term impact, not quick hacks. The real value comes from consistency where your content builds authority and compounds month after month.

What’s the investment?

Our packages typically start at $500 per month and scale based on the level of editing, strategy, and content output you need. Building a brand through high-performing video is a serious commitment, and we work with clients who see content as a growth driver, not just an expense.
